                theFoundationalDeity: "Oceania is a powerful and foundational deity within the cosmic structure of Eudoric and Eudoria, serving as the Mother Nature of Water. She is recognized as the Ocean Goddess, the sea's sovereign, and metaphorically, the Mother of all things water. Some don't even consider her a goddess. Without her, the world would not exist.",

