                eudoraIntervention: "When Naime figured out what was going on, she told Eudora. Eudora confronted Oceania, but Oceania only told Eudora, 'The ocean is MINE, not Eudora's.' When Eudora confessed to Naime that Oceania might be upset because of Tangaroa, Naime quickly broke up with Tangaroa, choosing Oceania over him.",

