                theTwentyYearExile: "During those 20 years, she adopted 42 children, some of whom were orphaned on the ruined island (the one she drowned on!). She made them sea guardians.",

                merlilyTheFavoriteDaughter: "One of her daughters, Merlily (her favorite), started dating Tangaroa. Feeling disgusted about this, Oceania chained Merlily to the bottom of the ocean, fearing her daughter would suffer the same heartache as her. She could hear her daughter trying to escape. One day, Merlily escaped with Tevye's help (he didn't know what he was doing!). Merlily went to see Tangaroa, who was married with children. Merlily was so mad that she tried to kill his family, which resulted in her death. Oceania was devastated, and she cried her eyes out. Tangaroa tried to apologize as Oceania cried over her daughter. She thought chaining Merlily away for over 40 years would help, but it only made things worse.",

